{"tid":2517764,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好無人好鍾意飲泰式奶茶","createTime":"2021-05-05T13:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T13:50:41.000Z","uid":395191,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cc419f8c8a2370b39ae851cf817eb496790758ee","tid":2517764,"uid":395191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:37:03.000Z","msg":"香港開台式奶茶嘅鋪頭就成行成市<br />\n但係真真正正做泰式奶茶嘅舖頭就好少<br />\n想拋磚引玉下 <br />\n平時飲開旺角西洋菜南果間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRoAZS1RNMKcnQ5gmb4XtsWwLBk7U94piod22fc92cY3n?filename=LbSeO1m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLbSeO1m.png&h=5ab33a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//每當有人飲泰式奶茶，心中都曾經有個疑問：「為什麼茶色是橘紅色的呢？」有人會答：「是色素。」也有人會選擇沉默&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n此時，須為泰茶平反。奶茶的橘紅是天然的，是泰國獨有的，也是一個茶葉品牌的故事。在泰國奶茶界，差不多被一個紅底金字商標的Cha Tra Mue茶葉所壟斷。這個品牌故事原來由華人揭開序章，在百多年前一個潮州茶商收購茗茶，再轉售給泰國當地的外國軍人，久而久之，茶葉和西方文化廣泛帶到皇室和街頭。有人會模仿西方混合牛奶的飲法，在泰國街頭更出現八角茴香和橙花水調味的變奏品。但對一向喜歡濃味的泰國人來說，外國西茶不是好味。於是Cha Tra Mue從茶商轉型，在泰北買田，以印度阿薩姆茶作茶種與其他茶葉混種，再配合一半發酵時間較短的紅茶和經長時間發酵的黑茶，調配出濃而不澀，帶香草味的泰式紅茶。加上當地長年下雨，濕潤的天氣導致土壤含有豐富的氧化鐵，使土質呈現酸性的紅土，所以種出來的茶也染上這層橘紅，塑造了泰國的特色。//"},{"pid":"241c9a8509d833fa75b33562464239d46504dc10","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"葵廣間泰讚了都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c755ff33d08e5f89a2431a97253a200962db26","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"葵廣有間黃店幾正 唔記得咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923e76ca085c0d09c30df939ac63ca5a5ee2ebca","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"241c9a8509d833fa75b33562464239d46504dc10","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"葵廣間泰讚了都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"畀你講咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1ad5689511bc213ddd6505cbc07c2e6cb84ef1","tid":2517764,"uid":395191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"241c9a8509d833fa75b33562464239d46504dc10","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"葵廣間泰讚了都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發覺好多泰國餐廳都無賣泰式奶茶<br />\n好似出名到忠誠呢類都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374782f3fe68e484d27af713e1a33add1f6dd9a3","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"923e76ca085c0d09c30df939ac63ca5a5ee2ebca","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"241c9a8509d833fa75b33562464239d46504dc10","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"葵廣間泰讚了都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"畀你講咗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:40:50.000Z","msg":"同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347192f1d645cc23ba492221732e7aed0d69ac87","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"374782f3fe68e484d27af713e1a33add1f6dd9a3","tid":2517764,"uid":266145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9