ore":0,"quote":{"pid":"cee398447eee21a33698d1afe9a96d46b0d967a9","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d9cf6b322613187295146a7c8d2a73304c39497","tid":2517764,"uid":395191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"347192f1d645cc23ba492221732e7aed0d69ac87","tid":2517764,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:42:10.000Z","msg":"利申本身唔鍾意港式台式奶茶 但原來泰式又幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:43:59.000Z","msg":"泰式種甜同純係好正<br />\n係其他茶做唔到<br />\n唔知點整"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:45:47.000Z","msg":"我都想學點整 葵芳好遠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T13:50:41.000Z","msg":"我有次見間餐廳 <br />\n佢整得好快<br />\n沖個茶底然後開罐唔知咩奶一撞落去就俾我<br />\n當然就唔係咁好味"}]}